Revision history for Search-OpenSearch-Engine-KSx

0.01    01 Feb 2010
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

0.02    22 Feb 2010
    * add Facet support

0.03    23 May 2010
    * use Search::Query::Dialect::KSx

0.04    22 June 2010
    * preserve multi-value fields as arrays in response.

0.05    25 July 2010
    * add logging

0.06    28 Oct 2010
    * bump KSx dependency to 0.16

0.07    30 Nov 2010
    * facet fetching fixes related to KS 0.31 API changes

0.08    07 Jan 2011
    * add REST API support

0.09    19 June 2011
    * logger dependent on debug() flag true
